种冲突可能加剧。 阿尔伯塔大学生物学教授安德鲁·德罗彻说，如果北极熊营养充足且状况良好，很少会给人类带来麻烦，但如果一只北极熊被困在陆地上且状况不佳，就很有可能引发冲突，并造成人类伤亡。 科学家艾丽莎·麦考尔也表示，北极熊很少攻击人类。通常情况下，北极熊远离人类居住地，喜欢在海上狩猎海豹。但气候变化导致气温波动、冰层破裂，有时迫使北极熊向内陆寻找食物。她称：「如果你被北极熊袭击，绝对不要装死，你应该尽你所能逃生。」加拿大一对夫妻被北极熊袭击，男子为保护妻子身受重伤 | 潇湘晨报网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-03e4e4437615f1cc6a730f41ce47ed49_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "10 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/6286390198"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIz6Cuwt3gteFWEAMaCTExMjIzNDAyMCCG49S6BjAAOHVAEnIKNjI4NjM5MDE5OHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1733850607.728321", "card_id": "Q_269141337", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 74}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价《叛逆的鲁鲁修》中的尤菲？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-476703dfc9b816f1c952194d4bf98ea4_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "5.6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/269141337"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iz6Cuwt3gteFWEAMaCDIyMDg0MzM0IMy2v9UFMAA48gFAE3IJMjY5MTQxMzM3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1733850607.728564", "card_id": "Q_5294387245", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 71}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "越接近考研越想放弃摆烂，这种心态该怎么办？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-e70d620e9c67307c81f1ea42a78d10df_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "5.3 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area